      "visual": ".cutready/visuals/b4d7165ea3de.json",
      "design_plan": "Simple placeholder visual, intentionally minimal. Narrative goal: summarize the three improvement paths, show they converge into one managed agent, and lightly hint at governance next. Hero metaphor: three small source cards feeding one larger managed agent card. Main objects: 1) title centered at top, 2) short subtitle beneath it, 3) three small rounded cards in a row on the left and center labeled Code + Data, Foundry, and M365 Feedback, 4) one larger hero card on the right labeled Managed Agent, 5) one small pill badge below the hero card that hints at Governance next. Layout: use the full 960x540 canvas with lots of breathing room; title around y 70, subtitle around y 105; three small cards around x 70, 250, 430 and y 220; hero card on the right around x 675 y 190; small governance badge below it around y 380. Colors: scene background $background; title in $title; subtitle in $subtitle; cards in $surface with $border; hero card accented with $accent; body labels in $foreground; supporting hint in $muted. Motion beats: very light stagger only -- title/subtitle fade in, then three cards, then simple arrows, then hero card, then governance badge."
